# 4. 話せない理由

Mafuyu: Miku, Rin...
Mafuyu: Is something the matter...?
Miku: <Kanade told me that you're resting because you're not feeling well.>
Rin: <Miku seemed really worried, so... I decided to join her.>
Mafuyu: I see...
Miku: <Are you okay?>
Miku: <You look a little distraught.>
Mafuyu: ...
Rin: <Did you have a bad dream or something...?>
Mafuyu: A bad...
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu: I'd say so...
Miku: <Mafuyu...>
Rin: <What was your dream about?>
Mafuyu: It was about that night...
Rin: <That night...?>
Mafuyu: Yes...
Mafuyu: When I told my mom how I really felt.
Miku: <Oh...>
Mafuyu: She refused to accept it...
Mafuyu: And then... My dad took her side...
Miku: <Your dad...?>
Miku: <But I thought he wasn't there that night.>
Mafuyu: He wasn't.
Mafuyu: But in my dream...
Mafuyu: He said he was so disappointed about me not wanting to become a doctor...
Miku: <Mafuyu...>
Rin: <That sounds like a really scary dream...>
Mafuyu: Scary...?
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu: (That night, I told my mom how I really felt, but she refused to understand...)
Mafuyu: (If my dad did the same thing...)
Miku: ...
Rin: Is Mafuyu gonna be okay?
Rin: She's been sleeping since then, but she still seemed a bit restless...
Miku: *Nod*
Miku: She's afraid that her dad won't understand...
Rin: ...
Rin: Which is keeping her from moving forward...
Miku: What...?
Rin: Mafuyu's been trying to move forward ever since she ran away from home that night...
Rin: But she's stuck...
Rin: What if her fear's preventing her from doing that...?
Rin: The fear of being rejected again.
Miku: Oh...
Rin: If that's the case...
Rin: I wanna help her.
Miku: Rin...
Rin: But I don't know how...
???: Hey, Rin!
Rin: That voice...
Mizuki: Heya! Oh, Miku's with you today.
Rin: What brings you here?
Mizuki: So, this new fabric shop opened up the other day!
Mizuki: And I got my hands on some of their stuff for really cheap. I was thinking that I could make ribbons for everyone!
Mizuki: I bet you guys are gonna love...
Mizuki: Hold on. Did something happen?
Miku: Oh, umm...
Mizuki: Is it about Mafuyu...? We heard that she isn't feeling well today and needs to rest.
Miku: Oh...
Miku: Yes, the thing is...
Mizuki: I see. So Mafuyu's...
Miku: *Nod*
Mizuki: ...
Mizuki: She's afraid that her dad won't understand...
Mizuki: (This must be the result of what she experienced that night...)
Mizuki: (When her mom refused to accept how her own daughter felt.)
Mizuki: (It had to have taken a ton of courage for Mafuyu to tell her the truth...)
Mizuki: (If her dad ends up taking her mom's side, then Mafuyu's going to be forced to suffer even more...)
Mizuki: (I think anyone would be scared of that prospect...)
Rin: Mizuki...?
Mizuki: Oh, sorry...
Mizuki: I sorta understand what Mafuyu's going through right now...
Rin: Huh...?
Mizuki: So, umm... To Mafuyu, her dad is a huge source of hope.
Mizuki: Him being family is probably a big reason why, but more importantly...
Mizuki: He seems to care a lot more about her well-being based on what I've been hearing about him recently.
Mizuki: Which is why it'd be awful if he were to go from being understanding to not...
Mizuki: There's even a chance that she'd end up in a worse situation than she is now.
Mizuki: Just thinking about it is pretty scary. Anyone would be petrified...
Rin: ...
Mizuki: (But...)
Mizuki: (Having someone who you know is on your side is huge...)
Mizuki: (If Mafuyu is also able to have someone like that... It'll give her a sense of security.)
Mizuki: So...
